name: Hey You! You talking to me? Wanna fight?
description: Poster - 33 unique characters having the time of their life, featuring some of my neurons in action plus Taxi Driver, Clockwork Orange, Robocop Killer robot, The Woman in Red, Jackie Chan The baseball guy from the Warriors, Steel Jeeg robot, The Bird of Heaven, Cupido, Barbara, Jack and Jill, Woman Commando, Dragon of Komodo man, Little annoying Punk amongst others
